Epol is in his own adventure to find his motorcycle back. His motorcycle was stolen by two thieves and Epol tries hard to find it back. Epol meet Azura, whose handbag was stolen by the same thieves! Unfortunately for Azura, in her hand contain a thumb drive that important for Tan Sri Bakhir, a wealthy businessman. Tan Sri Bakhir quickly offers Epol a sum of money; RM 50 000 if he finds the thieves and gives the thumb drive to the bank.
